title: Wall Street opens little changed, Fed in focus
text:
Tip : Use comma (,) to separate multiple quotes. Learn more... 
Mon, Oct 26, 2015, 14:00 GMT - UK Markets close in 2 hrs 30 mins Wall Street opens little changed, Fed in focus Reuters – 20 minutes ago Print 
REUTERS - U.S. stocks were little changed on Monday ahead of this week's Federal Reserve policy meeting and quarterly earnings reports from key companies including Apple. 
The Dow Jones industrial average rose 5.28 points, or 0.03 percent, to 17,651.98, the S&P 500 lost 0.7 points, or 0.03 percent, to 2,074.45 and the Nasdaq composite index dropped 1.02 points, or 0.02 percent, to 5,030.84.
